WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.836
It's 2041.

00:00:02.356 --> 00:00:05.516
The world is even stranger than fiction.

00:00:06.316 --> 00:00:11.236
Full of astonishing technologies
and scientific advances.

00:00:12.476 --> 00:00:16.276
But there's still one thing
that is very familiar.

00:00:16.956 --> 00:00:19.196
COVID is still with us.

00:00:20.756 --> 00:00:23.276
We've just figured out
how to live with it.

00:00:23.876 --> 00:00:27.676
You haven't been outside
of your apartment for three years.

00:00:29.076 --> 00:00:32.596
The pandemic of 2021 traumatized you.